sentence: Give me all Danish films.
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:country res:Denmark }

sentence: Give me the grandchildren of Bruce Lee.
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Bruce_Lee dbo:child ?child . ?child <http://dbpedia.org/property/children> ?uri }

sentence: Which state of the USA has the highest population density?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:densityrank ?rank } ORDER BY ASC(?rank) LIMIT 1

sentence: Which organizations were founded in 1950?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Organisation { ?uri dbo:formationYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:foundation ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:formation ?date } FILTER regex(?date, ^1950) }

sentence: Which state of the United States of America has the highest density?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbp:densityrank ?density } ORDER BY ASC(?density) LIMIT 1

sentence: Which spaceflights were launched from Baikonur?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/launchPad> res:Baikonur_Cosmodrome }

sentence: Give me a list of all trumpet players that were bandleaders.
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:occupation res:Bandleader ; dbo:instrument res:Trumpet }

sentence: How deep is Lake Placid?
sparqlQueGG: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lake_Placid_(Texas)> dbo:maximumDepth ?n }

sentence: Who is the tallest player of the Atlanta Falcons?
sparqlQueGG: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/team> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta_Falcons> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/height> ?h } ORDER BY DESC(?h) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
